SOURCE http://www.fico.com/en/blogs/uncategorized/artificial-intelligence-find-it-right-in-your-own-backyard/
AGENT FICO Falcon Fraud Management
GOAL Protects two thirds of the world’s payment card transactions against fraud.
DATA These models score transactions based on recent known fraud and non-fraud transaction data.
METHODS Falcon uses adaptive analytics, a type of machine learning in which self-learning models work with the Falcon consortium models to improve the prediction of future fraudulent behavior based on fraud attacks in production.
RESULTS It is able to score transactions in less than 60 milliseconds.
COMMENTS